.TH std::basic_filebuf::is_open 3 "Apr 19 2014" "1.0.0" "C++ Standard Libary"
.SH Synopsis
   bool is_open() const;

   Returns true if the most recent call to open() succeeded and there has been no call
   to close() since then.

